author: KEXP
description: With delicate sincerity, Michigan's Greet Death deliver a heavy set of fuzzy, dynamic rock on their third album 'Die in Love'. In-studio with host DJ Cheryl Waters, the band share a tender performance of "Country Girl" and more from the record.
title: Greet Death performs "Country Girl" and more Live on KEXP
